                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Olivares</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-05-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Acknowledges telegram of May 19 and states that he has communicated paraphrase
                    quoted to Madriz, who endeavored to sustain that his vessel sailed from a port
                    of the United States under straightforward circumstances. Adds that all
                    available military forces in his district are being hurried toward the Atlantic
                    coast.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
